{"tid":1533036,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普巴傷退法國 根度斯獲補選","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T22:12:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb324edc8f6793492f63070340bb9f2720c9314","tid":1533036,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】法國國家隊周一宣佈中場普巴因傷退隊，補選根度斯。<br />\n<br />\n普巴（Paul Pogba）在曼聯開季4場英超皆正選披甲，如常入選了法國領隊迪甘斯的大軍。不過，普巴在上場作客修咸頓的英超，於下半場扭傷了足踝，提早退下火線。<br />\n<br />\n這個傷患令普巴在周一退出國家隊，迪甘斯補選了阿仙奴中場根度斯。這名20歲小將今季於兵工廠大躍進，上場英超領軍以2:2逼和熱刺，表現廣受好評，終於首次獲得大國腳徵召。<br />\n<br />\n法國在今月國際賽期將出戰2場歐國盃外圍賽，先於7日主場迎戰阿爾巴尼亞，3日後同樣主場出擊，鬥安道爾。法國於H組暫時以4戰3勝1負9分排在榜首，由於今月的對手都是弱旅，相信全取6分的機會甚濃。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"9caac6ced8a1417debc7a5189712a8d601cb6a33","tid":1533036,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/7576676b9cbb7e708d96c5f0e65e2d1e/tumblr_px5wt8u5tv1vvwgg7o2_540.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F7576676b9cbb7e708d96c5f0e65e2d1e%2Ftumblr_px5wt8u5tv1vvwgg7o2_540.gif&h=e2b2eba4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e4532a72d01a2f544de4f157188555923823a9e","tid":1533036,"uid":204373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:35:43.000Z","msg":"拉比奧特？？？"},{"pid":"323f8b3b9dd2232bab9a8994f34823655a5281b0","tid":1533036,"uid":198245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:55:30.000Z","msg":"一個有英文一個無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9417a39ff97be2e1d21e110a29a1fce69972d85","tid":1533036,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:59:06.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: 